  * Major release v1.0.0 - Production ready
  * Multi-architecture support: AMD64 and ARM64/aarch64
  * Complete CI/CD pipeline with GitHub Actions
  * Cross-compilation support for Raspberry Pi and ARM servers
  * Enhanced systemd integration with configuration display
  * Comprehensive testing and documentation
  * Debian packaging with proper dependency handling
  * Professional installation and management scripts

